                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Baker</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-06-16">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">June</hi> 16, 1894</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The provisional Government of Salvador informs me that the President of the
                    United States has recognized that Government, and now ask extradition refugees.
                    Is it so? What shall I do?</p>
            </div>
